Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make an enemy of me,\NI'll make you pay for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vice Admiral Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Saul, who deserted\Nwith Olvia, is attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be burned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up! Preserve the books!\NWe have to pass down the history!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop them to the lake through the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be better than them being\Nburned up and gone! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul! Stop it now! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw the books out of the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save as many books as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preserve as many sentences as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that our predecessors' words from\Nthe past several thousand years...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will reach the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.75,0:01:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run to the evacuation ship while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can no longer survive\Nif you remain on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:30.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nholding our flag high in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:42.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cross this endless sea to go in search of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:48.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a global miracle no one\Nhas yet been able to find
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:53.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our hearts pounding,\Nwe'll just charge ahead as we please
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:59.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,following the footprints of\Nthose who chase their dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:06.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how stormy the night,\Nif we join our hearts as one,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:10.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we will be able to make it through
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:11.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:18.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nholding our flag high in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:24.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there are tears\Nwe don't want anyone to see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:30.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase it, chase it,\Nif we want to achieve our dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:33.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we should always look\Nstraight ahead without fear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:48.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nhead past everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:54.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as we don't run from it,\Nwe can grasp tomorrow in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:04:00.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase it, chase it,\Neverything we see before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:05.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's carve it into the blank pages of our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Brand New World
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Say You Want to Live! We Are Your Friends!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Hurry up and run!\NWhat was your mom's wish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sailing the evacuation ship out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Isn't that the monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she the daughter of Olvia,\Na criminal, who was in the paper before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! If we let her on the ship,\Nit might cause us trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! She's only a child!\NHurry up and get her on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuation ship! Don't let\Nthat brat come on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although she's a child, she's an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a target of our attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Spandine! I-Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? If we let her come on board,\Nwe'll be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be CP9! How absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Vice Admiral Saul is coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! I guess we didn't have to\Nask Olvia about his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire! Fire the cannons at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:05:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look good
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if a Buster Call is blocked by\Na former marine, now does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take pride in this attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't right! You should know it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're wiping out Ohara\Nto make an example of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is for the future of the world,\Nit can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, these scholars are\Nviolating the laws, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice changes its form\Ndepending on the position you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't criticize your sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're in our way, I can't let you be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The evacuation ship got blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was cannon fire! From one of the battleships!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was from Vice Admiral Sakazuki's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're gonna do it, we'll do it thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If even a single scholar is hiding\Non that ship by some chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the sacrifices made in this\Noperation will all be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to eradicate\Neven the possibility of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this something "justice" would do?!\NCan you still keep your head high?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to go as far as that idiot does!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna run, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's abnormally strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking a scholar with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Time Capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you stay on the island!\NSail out on my raft!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Saul?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for me. I got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There's no one on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alone now, but you'll\Nmeet friends someday for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is born into this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Robin! Don't look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're having a hard time,\Nlaugh like this, just like I taught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go meet the friends\Nwho're surely waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somewhere at sea, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live together with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also the history that humans chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How thoughtless humans are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even give you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...any parting words as a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tree of Knowledge... is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolute justice can\Nsometimes drive people mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to let you escape from this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth will sprout\Nfrom the seed Saul protected?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who you bear a grudge against is up to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for now, just be happy you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live as quietly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew lines on the sea with ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just go straight on that\Nsmall boat, you'll reach land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your enemy. I'll be the first to\Ncome after you if you cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom is on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that pain makes you want to die,\Nyou're free to do that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best library in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like books?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Robin's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud, Robin! Ohara is honorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot give up the future\Nyou young ones will live in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So laugh. When you're\Nhaving a hard time, just laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems stupid to laugh\Nwhen you're having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go meet the friends\Nwho're surely waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somewhere at sea, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no possibility of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are enough books\Nto fill the lake completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this by chance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is the brat!\NThere's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you find her?! Did you capture her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir! Keeping in mind to\Nlook out for "a suspicious girl,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we found a girl on a passenger\Nship that was leaving an island
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,far northeast of Ohara,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we lost her right after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got the devil's luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely saw a brat escaping\Nfrom burning Ohara on a small boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go after her, but the helm\Nsuddenly got stuck as if it was frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Mr. Saul must've let her\Nescape right before he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that she can decipher Poneglyphs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although she's still small, she's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This operation will go down\Nthe drain unless we capture her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as possible--I don't care how!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,79 million Berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a high bounty for an eight-year-old child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that she's a\Nsurvivor of those Ohara devils
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who planned the world's annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how, but they said\Nthat she sank six Navy battleships.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why her bounty is so high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the Government and\NNavy Headquarters are going after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed to have inherited the\Nideology of the executed scholars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a problem if she's left at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a child of the devil\Nwho shouldn't be allowed to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for always helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Thank you for letting me work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, before lunch, you have guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let her get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give me the money!\NI reported her to you, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She works very hard, although she's still small.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get up early tomorrow\Nmorning to go purchase stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good kid, but if we're\Nwith her, we'll be in danger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, look at this bounty amount!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey! She isn't in her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That little brat picked up on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I don't have any food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about you, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a wanted man, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do chores, I'll feed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Contact Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Robin?! Hand her over, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darn jinx!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sin is being alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Nico Robin is in this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find her! Hand her over to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found one...! A Poneglyph...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come inside! I've got nothing to sell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sixteen. I'll do anything.\NPlease let me be part of your organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed me, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin. I want you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you can read Poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... you exercise a Buster Call\Nright here, right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then together with Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you guys, too, will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we'd be eliminated\Nby our own people's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years ago,\Neverything was taken away from me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and many people's lives were ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was caused by a single attack--Buster Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That attack is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...targeted on the friends I was finally\Nable to find, whom I can be myself with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I wish to be with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more my fate will show its fangs to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far I go on the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a huge enemy that I can't shake off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the world and\Nits darkness are my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident with Aokiji, as well as this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already dragged you\Ninto my troubles twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this continues forever, even though\Nyou guys're good-natured...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll eventually feel that I'm a burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll betray me\None day and abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm most afraid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want\Nyou to come to rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to die someday anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That indeed is a sound argument!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. No one is stupid enough\Nto think that having you isn't a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that symbol, you damn pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That logo indicates the unity\Nof over 170 member countries
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,spanning the four seas and the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you now realize how completely\Npowerless you guys are to fight against it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how huge of an organization\Nthis woman has been pursued by?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now understand well the\Nidentity of Robin's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot through that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new weapon,\Na huge slingshot... named Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good look at its power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack... Firebird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They've gone and done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they understand what it\Nmeans to attack the flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirates declared war\Nagainst the World Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?! Don't think\Nthat you'll be able to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after making the entire world your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't heard you say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To live...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be allowed\Nto live in this world, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence itself is a huge crime, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was something I dared not wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever let me wish for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... it's really okay for me\Nto utter my wish for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the sea with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...! I love you guys, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:17.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight harder against\Nthe wall that confronts us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:20.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We charge ahead stronger\Nwith overflowing power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:25.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't fear even if we\Nhave to give up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:28.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's all to ensure we smile in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:31.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll become No. 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:33.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll aim for freedom in wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:35.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's a faint light\Nshowing us the road to tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:37.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,an era created by risking everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.60,0:22:39.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We always try our best, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:41.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we want to achieve glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:43.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,now is the time--don't be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:45.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll surely win the future\Ntogether with friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:48.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we start running faster\Ntowards the vast world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:52.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take off with unknown powers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:55.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't fear, and we don't waver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:22:58.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\Nin the end we'll surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:03.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight harder against\Nthe wall that confronts us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:06.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We charge ahead stronger\Nwith overflowing power
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:11.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't fear even if we\Nhave to give up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:13.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:15.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start running towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:18.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's all to ensure we smile in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, I swore that I'd\Ngather a crew and become a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like the pirate who protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, just like he protected me\Nthat time, I'll protect you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already one of us, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna rescue you without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jump Towards the Falls! Luffy's Feelings!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
